  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to develop an integrated therapy (physical therapy and psychotherapy) to treat
      cognitive distortion for body image. Then, validate its efficacy to make an improvement in
      both physical and mental health.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
